# NAPCO Nucleus — per-developer config.
#
# DEVELOPERS DO NOT NEED ANY SECRETS.
# The agent host (MVPACCESS) owns every Gmail / Drive / API credential.
# Each dev machine only pushes Teams chat + call recordings + downloaded
# attachments to the central SMB share, using your normal Windows AD
# login for share access.
#
# Fill in the values below. Save and close Notepad to continue setup.

# UNC path to the team's central share on MVPACCESS.
NUCLEUS_CENTRAL_PATH=\\MVPACCESS\nucleus

# OPTIONAL: how your folder is labeled on central. Defaults to your
# Windows username. Set this if you want a friendlier label.
# NUCLEUS_DEV_NAME=Yourname

# OPTIONAL: comma-separated extra dirs to search for downloaded Teams
# chat attachments. Defaults to your ~/Downloads (and any Teams
# subfolders it auto-creates). Override only if your browser/Teams
# saves files somewhere unusual.
# NUCLEUS_DOWNLOADS_PATH=C:\Users\you\Downloads,D:\Shared\Teams-Files
